productdetail.Name: advanced Electric Lint Remover (Bhur Remover) Removes lint from All Woolens Sweaters, Blankets, Jackets (Set of 1)
productdetail.About: Quick and efficient Switch to turn it on and gently run the shaving head over the surface of the clothes.Corded The lint remover runs on an inbuilt battery and has a corded wire.Battery operated lint removers run out of power after a few times of use but you save hundreds on batteries with this corded lint remover. Smart design With large shaving head, detachable lint catcher and comfort grip handle.Slide downward to release the lint catcher gently to remove and clean the collected lint.The comfort grip handle allows the lint remover to fit comfortably in your hand, giving you a good and control as you de- fuzz your garments. Dual protection The adjustable height spacer protects your garments from being cut or snagged or caught.It also protects and reinforces your hands from accidentally touching the shaver foil.A cleaning brush is included in the pack to help you easily clean your appliance after use. Superior quality product
